snippet.title: Just Cause 4: Rico's Rival [PEGI]
snippet.description:
Subscribe to our channel for more content on Just Cause 4!  http://sqex.link/JCSubscribe

Meet Gabriela Morales: Leader of the infamous Black Hand, and Rico's toughest adversary yet. 

Just Cause 4 is coming to Xbox One, PlayStation 4 and Windows PC on 4th December 2018.
